Pre-requisites for running MPI code

The included code was intended for Windows.
The following link includes a guide on how to configure MS-MPI (a derivation from MPICH2)
for MS Visual Studio, if you haven't already configured MPI for your machine.
There is also a link on where to download MS-MPI from Microsoft.

http://www.math.ucla.edu/~mputhawala/PPT.pdf
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/message-passing-interface/microsoft-mpi
